title: Act1_EveIntro_PostCombat_P1N1_Alt
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: You actually did it. Are you a Hunter?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Yup.

A distant roar is heard. (TODO play sound via function here)

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: We shouldn’t stay here, if a stronger Meminiscor shows up we’re in trouble.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Got it.
Cyrus: Don’t have to tell me twice.
